match.name: Sundowner II
match.about: This match is the follow up match to the Sundowner that was cut short by severe weather.  There is no charge to attend.  We will be shooting 3 stages in the evening hours and then finishing up the 5 night stages that we were not allowed to shoot in the original Sundowner match.
